CS||CP||fp||at|^B@2^Y@3T|FP||AT|he Grand Coup is the most publicized - the most widely talked about - of all the trump coups. The play has gained a reputation that it does not deserve, for it is far from being a very useful play. Actually, the mechanics of it are fairly simple, for it is merely a trump-shortening play with the additional feature that the shortening is brought about by the deliberate ruffing of 1 or 2^*I winners^*N.|
