{    TRUMP COUPS IN GENERAL    }
^-|
CS||cp||fp||at|^B@2^Y@3T|FP||AT|he trump coup is not confined to situations in which only one honor is missing. Even what seems like a rather innocuous combination of cards, such as that in the following diagram, may present a coup situation:|
